column1: Certain restrictions may apply.  Quantity restrictions and associated pricing with the LRMC Pharmacy Discount Drug List may apply and any final prices for a prescription, if any, will be determined by the LRMC Pharmacy location that is processing the prescription.  LRMC Pharmacy reserves the right to modify the terms of, and drugs covered by, the LRMC Pharmacy Discount Drug List at any time without prior or proper notice.  LRMC Pharmacy may limit drugs offered on the LRMC Pharmacy Discount Drug List to drugs that are in stock and that are manufactured and sold by certain pharmaceutical manufacturers.  The LRMC Pharmacy Discount Drug List is not a discount prescription drug plan, discount drug card, membership drug program, or insurance plan.  The LRMC Pharmacy Discount Drug List cannot be combined with other offers, discounts, rebates, or promotions.  In order for a patient to obtain a drug from a LRMC Pharmacy location the prescription being filled must be 340B eligible.
